  "plateau": {
    "description": "Authoritative building tier — 国土交通省 Project PLATEAU (2020 tokyo23ku CityGML, LOD1): footprints (bldg:lod0RoofEdge) + measuredHeight, 1,410,692 buildings across Tokyo's 23 special wards. SEPARATE source and licence from the OSM tier above. Split into 572 per-1km-mesh packs (Japanese 3rd-level mesh) for viewport-culled 3D rendering — a single all-wards pack would far exceed deck.gl's ~100k-polygon frame budget.",
    "source": "Project PLATEAU (国土交通省 / MLIT)",
    "license": "ODbL-1.0",
    "attribution": "出典：国土交通省 PLATEAU（加工して作成）",
