    "tier": "flat",
    "mesh": "Japanese 3rd-level (~1 km, 8-digit code)",
    "buildings": 1410692,
    "tallest_m": 332.9,
    "format": "served brotli-only (<tier>.<hash>.topo.json.br) — decode client-side; raw .topo.json not published. Each building carries its PLATEAU measuredHeight (m). Resolve packs.plateau/index.json -> meshes[].pack against the geo-data base URL."
